<html lang='ko'>
    <head>
        <meta charset='utf-8' />
        <title>Authorize Page</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; /* 밝은 배경 */ color: #333; margin: 0;
            padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }
            .consent-container { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 24px 48px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px
            8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); width: 360px; max-width: 90%; } h1 { color: #5c5c5c; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom:
            12px; } p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; } ul { list-style: none; padding: 0;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0; } li { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 8px; }
            .button-group { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; } button { flex: 1; margin: 0 8px; padding:
            12px; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #ffffff; border: none;
            border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; transition: background-color 0.3s; } .btn-accept { background-color:
            lightskyblue; } .btn-decline { background-color: gray; } button:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='consent-container'>
            <h1>Been's OAuth 권한 요청</h1>
            <p>애플리케이션이 귀하의 계정 정보에 접근하고자 합니다. 다음 권한을 허용하시겠습니까?</p>
            <ul>
                <li>프로필 정보 읽기</li>
                <li>이메일 주소 접근</li>
            </ul>
            <div class='button-group'>
                <form method='POST' action='/auth/authorize'>
                    <input type='hidden' name='client_id' value={{client_id}} />
                    <input type='hidden' name='redirect_uri' value='{{redirect_uri}}' />
                    <input type='hidden' name='scope' value='{{scope}}' />
                    <input type='hidden' name='state' value='{{state}}' />
                    <input type='hidden' name='response_type' value='{{response_type}}' />
                    <button type='submit' class='btn-accept' name='action' value='approve'>승인</button>
                    <button type='submit' class='btn-decline' name='action' value='deny'>거부</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>